caption.body: Next Saturday, November 16, SFO Museum is presenting a free lecture and guided tour to coincide with our exhibition “The Intriguing World of Insects”. A lecture by Dr. Peter Oboyski, curator of the Essig Museum of Entomology at UC Berkeley, begins at 1:00 at the Aviation Museum and Library, and the guided tour of the exhibition will follow. Kindly RSVP for the lecture by November 14 to curator@flysfo.com. For more information on this event, please see our website:  http://bit.ly/SFOMEvents
